PrecisRe-appointment of RENÉE MARCELLE BOURASSA, of Toronto, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Toronto Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour, for a term of three years, effective June 14, 1997.
